

5️⃣ Configure Azure DevOps Secrets
Go to Project Settings > Pipelines > Library or use variable groups to set:

ARM_CLIENT_ID
ARM_CLIENT_SECRET
ARM_SUBSCRIPTION_ID
ARM_TENANT_ID

These are values from a Service Principal with Contributor access.



az ad sp create-for-rbac --role="Contributor" --scopes="/subscriptions/<your-subscription-id>"
